<subSubSection id="69FF6505EB428B044CA440A5FBCDFE7E" pageId="5" pageNumber="299" type="description">
<paragraph id="215A368EEB428B044CA440A5FEB7FF7D" blockId="5.[136,284,157,183]" box="[136,284,157,183]" pageId="5" pageNumber="299">
<heading id="7A1281E2EB428B044CA440A5FEB7FF7D" bold="true" box="[136,284,157,183]" fontSize="11" level="1" pageId="5" pageNumber="299" reason="1">
<emphasis id="1391EA9CEB428B044CA440A5FEB7FF7D" bold="true" box="[136,284,157,183]" pageId="5" pageNumber="299">Description:</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="215A368EEB428B044CA440DEFBCDFE7E" blockId="5.[136,1452,230,437]" pageId="5" pageNumber="299">
The plant forms a shrub, which is 
<quantity id="E61D9B6BEB428B044DD640DEFD93FECA" box="[506,568,230,256]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.4" pageId="5" pageNumber="299" unit="m" value="1.4">1.4 m</quantity>
wide and about 
<quantity id="E61D9B6BEB428B044EC640DEFC83FECA" box="[746,808,230,256]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.0" pageId="5" pageNumber="299" unit="m" value="0.6">0.6 m</quantity>
tall. Primary branches are usually 
<quantity id="E61D9B6BEB428B04488E40DEFAA4FECA" box="[1186,1295,230,256]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.5" metricValueMax="7.0" metricValueMin="6.0" pageId="5" pageNumber="299" unit="cm" value="65.0" valueMax="70.0" valueMin="60.0">60–70 cm</quantity>
long, covered by 3–4 secondary branches (preferably 1–2). The branches branch at this angle. Many secondary branches thicken the shrub’s foliage too much. Leaf-blade is rounded base and without a pronounced tip. The top of the leaf is rounded. Leaf border shallowly serrated. Leaf base is rounded and wedge-shaped. Stipules are large kidney-shaped, with notched edging. The fruit is round, barrel-shaped, ripens three weeks after ‘Alfa’. The fruit cup is almost completely overgrown. Fruits are medium-sized and weigh 
<quantity id="E61D9B6BEB428B044E8D41A2FD54FE7E" box="[673,767,410,437]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="kg" metricValue="6.0" metricValueMax="7.0" metricValueMin="5.0" pageId="5" pageNumber="299" unit="g" value="60.0" valueMax="70.0" valueMin="50.0">50–70 g</quantity>
. Fruit dimensions: 47 × 
<quantity id="E61D9B6BEB428B04483C41A2FBC9FE7E" box="[1040,1122,410,436]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.6" pageId="5" pageNumber="299" unit="mm" value="46.0">46 mm</quantity>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
